parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Turn Signal and Hazard Light Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turn signals and hazard lights can increase the risk of accidents, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intentions, leading to potential collisions.
symptoms: The turn signals and hazard lights work intermittently
or become inoperative. The hazard switch may fall through the dashboard
and the lights may stay on even when the switch is turned off.

and the vehicle hesitates to start.
